        Common Styles

        Error Indicators
        .k-invalid,
        .error-field,
        .input-error {
            border: 1px solid red !important;
        }

        Fixed error-border class that was incomplete
        .error-border {
            border: 1px solid red !important;
        }

        Some error styles have different border width, keeping this specific one
